```sql
-- Deduplicated billing events, one row per subscription/month
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        subscription_id,
        event_month,
        amount,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY subscription_id, event_month
            ORDER BY event_id DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_billing_events') }}
)
SELECT
    subscription_id,
    event_month,
    amount
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

```sql
-- Monthly subscription metrics by tier and industry
WITH enriched AS (
    SELECT
        sp.subscription_id,
        sp.user_id,
        sp.tier,
        uc.industry,
        b.event_month,
        b.amount
    FROM {{ ref('int_subscription_plan') }} sp
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_user_company') }} uc
        ON uc.user_id = sp.user_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_billing') }} b
        ON b.subscription_id = sp.subscription_id
)
SELECT
    event_month AS month,
    tier,
    industry,
    COUNT(DISTINCT subscription_id) AS active_subscriptions,
    SUM(amount) AS total_mrr,
    COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS unique_users
FROM enriched
GROUP BY
    event_month,
    tier,
    industry
ORDER BY
    event_month,
    tier,
    industry
```
